title: Black Crowes on MTV's Unplugged
description:
The Southern Rock of the Black Crowes takes a different twist in this MTV special: Black Crowes Unplugged. With the band finally getting their shit together and perform the way they should, this may be one for the classic archives.

Songs include "Sting Me", "Wiser Time", "Locust Street", and more. This show runs 42:22 and has a few cut aways to the band commenting on their outlook and music.
